Types::Standard::StrMatch(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation Types::Standard::StrMatch(3)

NAME

Types::Standard::StrMatch - internals for the Types::Standard StrMatch type constraint

STATUS

This module is considered part of Type-Tiny's internals. It is not covered by the Type-Tiny stability policy.

DESCRIPTION

This file contains some of the guts for Types::Standard. It will be loaded on demand. You may ignore its presence.

BUGS
